Damien never said Guide abuse never happened.  Unfortunately, there are very few Guides who do abuse the system.  Fortunately, these are few and far between.  Guides are screened during their Apprentice training.  Should a Guide be caught breaking the rules and policies set by Verant, such as Severine was, then the consequences are typically severe and could lead to dismissal from the Program.  One must, after all, be accountable for one's actions.<br>
